---

## ✅ 7. Preventative Measures

- Conduct quarterly phishing simulations  
- Require MFA for all logins  
- Keep systems updated (auto-patching enabled)  
- Weekly security log reviews by internal staff  
- Role-based access control (RBAC) enforced

